{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1636902501.244252","card_id":"Q_464242642","target":{"id":464242642,"title":"你知道哪些过去 100 年里「说到做到」的故事？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/464242642","type":"question","created":1623298557,"answer_count":298,"follower_count":2411,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[922,4014,5582,12230,719914],"comment_count":46,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"有人说，「说到做到」这四个字既浪漫又踏实。 「全面建成小康社会，一个民族不能少；实现中华民族伟大复兴，一个民族也不能少。共产党说到就要做到，也一定能够做到。」 过去100年来，那些许下的诺言一一兑现：从脱贫攻坚， 反腐倡廉，城市新颜换旧颜，到全民医保、探火探月、条条道路通故乡… 建党百年之际，央视新闻联合知乎发起主题提问，邀请各位知友来分享：你所知道、所经历、所深受影响的「说到做到」的故事，你的回答可能登上央视新闻！"},"attached_info":"ClUIksq0z/TK3dkGEAMaCDY1NDQ0NTY5IP2jhoYGMC446xJAAHIJNDY0MjQyNjQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"1787 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-997aa889499068df0c8f49964cd49f7a_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1636902501.245157","card_id":"Q_498681974","target":{"id":498681974,"title":"河南 9 岁男童一提上学就发烧近 40℃，多次去医院检查都未发现病因，可能是什么原因造成的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/498681974","type":"question","created":1636801426,"answer_count":309,"follower_count":1151,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[988,1576,2099,4080,18012],"comment_count":67,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，河南商丘，9岁男童轩轩总是发烧到快40℃，最高发烧到42℃，这种状态持续了近半年，期间家人多次带他去医院检查，甚至拍了CT做了骨髓穿刺都没有发现病因。更让人疑惑的是，十有八九只要提到上学，轩轩就会高烧。9岁男童一提上学就发烧快40℃ 医生：排除感染引起的发烧"},"attached_info":"Cj8Iksq0z/TK3dkGEAMaCDczMDk5Mzk1IJK3vowGMEM4/whAAXIJNDk4NjgxOTc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"761 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-112e6d54a25a3