ard_id":"Q_305767144","target":{"id":305767144,"title":"艺术作品对于人类的意义究竟是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/305767144","type":"question","created":1544805605,"answer_count":105,"follower_count":655,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[69,2058,6560,13576,28211],"comment_count":7,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"例如历史的意义在于它可以记录我们人类之前发生过的事情；物理的意义在于探索万物的奥秘，并改进我们的生存环境，让我们生活的更加便利；设计的意义在于是一种有目的的艺术活动；但是对于艺术作品呢？它只是为了展现艺术家心中的世界或思想？？ 在备课的时候突然想如何让学生理解那些伟大艺术家们的作品。例如最近的课程里讲到的如梵高、莫奈、葛饰北斋等等那些艺术大家他们留下的这些艺术瑰宝对于我们人类来说究竟有什么意义？诚然这些艺术家的作品都具有无与伦比的艺术造诣，尤其是在上野西洋美术馆见到过雷诺阿、莫奈等那些些大师的真迹后，除了叹为观止和憋在心里的卧槽牛逼！之外的震撼还能带给了我们什么。PS：没有诋毁任何艺术作品或否认艺术作品存在价值的意思！！！只是为了想让学生更加了解那些作品的伟大。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Iksq0z/TK3dkGEAMaCDMwMjI0NDMwIOW5z+AFMAc4jwVAKXIJMzA1NzY3MTQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-bf03b5f0b4acecb2a151e1a9add3247f_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"42_1636902501.2652037","card_id":"Q_439194875","target":{"id":439194875,"title":"大家有什么简单方便的速食推荐？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/439194875","type":"question","created":1610528077,"answer_count":134,"follower_count":648,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,568,1746,2566,8458],"comment_count":7,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Iksq0z/TK3dkGEAMaCDU5ODc2OTIwIM3q+v8FMAc4iAVAKnIJNDM5MTk0ODc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-24ed8cf5b51eab0cb870ff56c3f5cf50_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"43_1636902501.26559","card_id":"Q_23836220","target":{"id":23836220,"title":"家中有猫，出门的时候总是一